content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 78.10 - Compliance with Federal aviation administration rules and regulations required

State Regulations

No person shall land an aircraft upon, fly an aircraft
from, or conduct any other aircraft operations on or from the airport other
than in conformity with the current Federal Aviation Administration rules and
regulations. Notes
